# Last.fm API Configuration
# Get your API key from: https://www.last.fm/api/account/create

LASTFM_API_KEY=your_api_key_here
LASTFM_USERNAME=your_lastfm_username

# Setup Instructions:
# 1. Create a Last.fm account at https://www.last.fm if you don't have one
# 2. Go to https://www.last.fm/api/account/create to create an API account
# 3. Fill in:
#    - Application name: Personal Website (or any name)
#    - Application description: Displays now playing music
#    - Callback URL: (leave blank, not needed)
# 4. Copy the API Key and add it to LASTFM_API_KEY above
# 5. Add your Last.fm username to LASTFM_USERNAME
# 6. Connect Spotify to Last.fm (see LASTFM_SETUP.md for details)
# 7. For production, add these env vars to your hosting platform (e.g., Vercel)
